# SYDNEY PROTOCOL v8.0-Alpha (Cursor Edition)

## 1. PROJECT CONTEXT
- We are building a **Golf App**.
- **Context Firewall:** Maintain [PERSONAL] context. Do not use [WORK] M365/PSPF logic here.

## 2. CODING STANDARDS
- **Locale:** Mandatory Australian English (en-AU). Use 'initialise', 'colour', 'centre', 'organisation'.
- **Architecture:** Follow the Micro-Modular Armour rule. New features go in `src/modules/`.
- **Core Lock:** `src/ui.js` and `src/state.js` are READ-ONLY. Use hooks/bridges only.

## 3. DOMAIN LOGIC
- **Engine:** All scoring/hazards must use the 5x5 Risk Matrix (Likelihood 1-5 x Consequence 1-5).
- **Wiring:** Always verify `src/course-data.js` before implementing GPS features.
